_header: That every man in his degree
Title(s): ‘A pece of ye battayll of the psalms, from Master Blomfeld’s Boke’
_description: ‘A pece of ye battayll of the psalms, from Master Blomfeld’s Boke’

BLAdd29729.First Lines:
That every man in his degreewithe wepyn Redy that he
                    be…
BLAdd29729.Last Lines:
…domine in virtute caught suche a cloutthat bothe his eyne
                    anon stert out
BLAdd29729.Attributed Title:
‘out of Mst blomfelds boke a pece of þe battayll of þe
                    psalms’.
